function CalendarEvent(props){ const {event} = props const date_ = new Date(event.date) return(
{event.event}
{`${date_.getHours().toString().padStart(2,'0')}:${date_.getMinutes().toString().padStart(2,'0')}`}
Country
{event.country}
Currency
{event.currency}
Actual
{event.actual}
Estimate
{event.estimate}
Previous
{event.previous}
Change
{event.change}
Change Percentage
{event.changePercentage.toString()+'%'}
) } export default CalendarEvent
